2.  The user typing "智谱" (Zhipu) into the search bar and performing the search.

5.  The final scene is the homepage of the Zhipu AI website, showcasing its "Z.ai GLM Large Model Open Platform".

Essentially, the video demonstrates a user searching for information about the Chinese AI company Zhipu and navigating to its official website.
